## Memory Operations

### Session Start

```
1. detect_project_context() â†’ Analyze current working directory and file context
2. analyze_session_requirements() â†’ Determine if memory access or cross-session persistence needed
3. conditional_serena_activation() â†’ Only activate if memory operations required
