   - Simple task start â†’ Skip activation for performance
4. list_memories() â†’ Show existing task state from correct project (if activated)
5. read_memory("current_plan") â†’ Resume context with project awareness (if activated)
6. think_about_collected_information() â†’ Understand where we left off with proper project context
```

